{"tid":1538604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"徹回就算，當手足係condom?","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:25:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T07:50:36.000Z","uid":177620,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8b646a8670fe8fc045b36a10000ee2b5632dd307","tid":1538604,"uid":177620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:25:10.000Z","msg":"我地成功爭取徹回，係有賴大家一齊抗爭，依家徹回咗法案就由得同志被人告？仲有冇人性？用完即棄？<br />\n被人射眼打傷嘅付出咗，成果就我地收，自唔自私咗啲？<br />\n更何況一單還一單，狗賊濫權，政府腐敗都未算清，好意思講收貨？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">9月7機場見<br />\n9月8美領見</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1089ac965a3a422b70128c4ee874a39daf0a6346","tid":1538604,"uid":177620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:25:33.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"8720884bd512336b0a670b2547ef32a9d485c5b0","tid":1538604,"uid":177620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:26:03.000Z","msg":"每星期六都要幫機場做交通測試呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e4b34ec3cb035c642980cd2c767755c14948fcd","tid":1538604,"uid":177620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:26:22.000Z","msg":"呢場仗未贏架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484077c1cb496462fa086d71b4ace1587683f28c","tid":1538604,"uid":241210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:26:50.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"d2e39931f1d5133e4593ac58d5d1f9580417095e","tid":1538604,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:26:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da7d55d887d97e16c55f77038d2b83ccd1cc58d6","tid":1538604,"uid":177620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:26:58.000Z","msg":"唔好忘記默默付出嘅前線呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c1ae4eeea5100bb14c7857cbdba3a6e3faf1ed","tid":1538604,"uid":161463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:27:05.000Z","msg":"推啊啊啊一齊黎一齊走!"},{"pid":"683087ce4966163664a0666f16a23ff31158fd82","tid":1538604,"uid":134107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:28:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kybLqX5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkybLqX5.jpg&h=ae2d5f1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n入嚟幫手推<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n[10月1送大禮]「和理拍」一齊推上聯合國人權理事會！！!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536307</a>"},{"pid":"d927298216a2cdc4c7109688f3250c16568383ac","tid":1538604,"uid":177620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:28:17.000Z","msg":"講好咗一齊除口罩相聚架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset